<p>
<note n="0058001" resp="#resp1" place="foot text" type="orig" target="#nkr_note_orig_0058001">萬佳（Vaṅga）是今之孟伽拉（Bengal）。</note>
<note n="0058002" resp="#resp1" place="foot text" type="orig" target="#nkr_note_orig_0058002">師子邑（Sīhapura）恐今之 Sīhar（高桑駒吉著，東南印度諸國之研究三四二頁）。</note>
<note n="0058003" resp="#resp1" place="foot text" type="orig" target="#nkr_note_orig_0058003">Lāḷa 之音寫。為今之 Gujerat（高桑前揭書三四一頁）。</note>
<note n="0058004" resp="#resp1" place="foot text" type="orig" target="#nkr_note_orig_0058004">本文 paricārikā 是 paricārake？</note>
<note n="0059005" resp="#resp1" place="foot text" type="orig" target="#nkr_note_orig_0059005">本文 honti sabbe adassanaṁ 是 yantu sabbe adassanaṁ？</note>
<note n="0059006" resp="#resp1" place="foot text" type="orig" target="#nkr_note_orig_0059006">本文 āgamicchati 為 āgacchantu？</note>
<note n="0059007" resp="#resp1" place="foot text" type="orig" target="#nkr_note_orig_0059007">原語 Naggadīpan 是裸露者，即兒童等島之意。</note>
<note n="0059008" resp="#resp1" place="foot text" type="orig" target="#nkr_note_orig_0059008">原語 Mahilāraṭṭha 女婦人等國之意。</note>
<note n="0059009" resp="#resp1" place="foot text" type="orig" target="#nkr_note_orig_0059009">本文 apilavantā 是 pilavantāva。</note>
<note n="0059010" resp="#resp1" place="foot text" type="orig" target="#nkr_note_orig_0059010">Suppāra 之音譯，在印度之西海岸，為今之 Sopāra 在 Bombay 之北 Thāna 洲。其詳細之考證見高桑前揭書三二一頁以下。</note>
<note n="0059011" resp="#resp1" place="foot text" type="orig" target="#nkr_note_orig_0059011">本文 nabajjhakā 是 na-budhya-ka？</note>
<note n="0059012" resp="#resp1" place="foot text" type="orig" target="#nkr_note_orig_0059012">原語 Tambapaṇṇi 銅葉之義，指錫蘭。</note>
<note n="0059013" resp="#resp1" place="foot text" type="orig" target="#nkr_note_orig_0059013">原語 Uppalavaṇṇa 毘瑟笯（Viṣṇu）之事。</note>
<note n="0060014" resp="#resp1" place="foot text" type="orig" target="#nkr_note_orig_0060014">Bhārukaccha（SktḄharukaccha）之音譯，相當今之 Bharoch（or Broach）港。</note>
<note n="0060015" resp="#resp1" place="foot text" type="orig" target="#nkr_note_orig_0060015">本文 ukkhittavāta 是 ukkhittā vāt？</note>
<note n="0060016" resp="#resp1" place="foot text" type="orig" target="#nkr_note_orig_0060016">本文 padasāgamanaṁ jayati 是 padasāgamanaṁ jhāyati。</note>
<note n="0060017" resp="#resp1" place="foot text" type="orig" target="#nkr_note_orig_0060017">本文 nāvaṁ anurakkhena ca 是 Anurādhanakkhattena ca？</note>
<note n="0060018" resp="#resp1" place="foot text" type="orig" target="#nkr_note_orig_0060018">本文 paṭhaman to idh'āgato 是 pṭhaman te idhâgatā？</note>
<note n="0060019" resp="#resp1" place="foot text" type="orig" target="#nkr_note_orig_0060019">本文 bahū sabbe 是 bahu sattā？</note>
<note n="0060020" resp="#resp1" place="foot text" type="orig" target="#nkr_note_orig_0060020">就此等聚落遺跡之考證見大王統史第七章四三～四五 Paker. Ancient Ceylon VIII. Mitton. The lost cities of Ceylon p. 235 ff。</note>
<note n="0060021" resp="#resp1" place="foot text" type="orig" target="#nkr_note_orig_0060021">本文 samāpatti 是 samāpattiṁ？</note>
</p>
